Name: Jellyfish Season
About the game: 'Jellyfish Season' is a very short visual novel. The parable tells about people trying to find themselves in life. You have to play for a fat man named Niklas, who meets a strange girl on the tropical beach. She writes poetry and says that she is ... dead. There is no choices in the game. Only one beach. One girl. Lots of jellyfish.
